ey show that the\nenvironment around protostars is better modeled considering processed samples\nand, consequently, demonstrates the chemical evolution of the astrophysical\nices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Apr 2015 04:17:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-01"}
