ion and condensation cycles. We\nthus witness simultaneously widespread cooling and TNE. Finally, we discuss the\nimplications of our new observations for both static and impulsive heating\nmodels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Apr 2015 09:03:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Aug 2015 16:11:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-27"}
